<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.6">
<l>eñcāven narakat taḻunti naṭuṅkukiṉṟēṟ</l>
<l>kañcēleṉ ṟaṭiyē ṉaiyāṭkoḷ ḷavallāṉai</l>
<l>neñcēnī niṉaiyā tiṟaippoḻutu miruttikaṇṭāy</l>
<l>mañcārmā ḷikaicūḻ vayalā limaintaṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, you see, you [must] remain for only a second without thinking</l>
<l>Of that man of Āli, its fields encircled by mist-covered mansions,</l>
<l>The one who is able to take me, his servant, into his service</l>
<l>Saying, “Don’t fear,” to me who is trembling, sinking into unceasing fiery hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
